# =============================================================================
#  PSID_SHELF — files intentionally NOT published to GitHub
# =============================================================================

# --- Raw & derived microdata --------------------------------------------------
#  PSID and NLSY are distributed under data-use agreements that prohibit public
#  redistribution; these files also exceed GitHub's 100 MB/file limit. Only code,
#  aggregate result graphs and write-ups are published. See README "Data availability".
*.dta
*.csv
*.dat
*.sav
*.sas7bdat
*.sdf
*.cdb
*.dct
*.NLSCROSS
*.NLSY79

# --- Data stored in Office/Excel formats (microdata extracts) ----------------
#  Excluded for the same reasons as .dta/.csv. NOTE: this deliberately does NOT
#  exclude the variable-selection crosswalks under setup_framework/keyDocs/ and
#  code/data_prep/ — those document the variable-selection work and are kept.
**/data/**/*.xlsx
06_Employment/employment_monthly_data.xlsx

# --- Raw third-party survey extracts (NLS Investigator downloads) ------------
02_NLSY79/extracts/

